"\n"
"<p>\n"
"The first column must contain the article number of the desired product.<br /"
">\n"
"The second (fourth, sixth... and other even ones) is the name of the "
"property.<br />\n"
"The third (fifth, seventh... and other odd ones) is the value of the "
"property.<br />\n"
